import React from 'react'

import image2 from './IMG/image2.png'
import image3 from './IMG/image3.jpg'

function App() {
    return(
        <>
            <Header 
              list='Home' list2='About'
              titulo="React" 
                          
              button="Login" 
              button2='Register'  
              
            />
              
              <Content title={'Seja Bem-Vindos 2022 React.js UP'}>

                        image={image1}
                        titulo="Techs"
                        paragrafo="ccessible. Provide a valid, navigable address as the href value.

                    />

                    <Card 
                        image={image2}
                        titulo="Techs 2"
                        paragrafo="ccessible. Provide a valid, navigable address as the href value.
                        If you cannot provide a valid href, but still need the e"
                    />
                    
                    <Card 
                        image={image3}
                        titulo="Techs 3"
                        paragrafo="ccessible. Provide a valid, navigable address as the href value.
                        If you cannot provide a valid href, but still need the e"
                    />

                </Cards>

              </Content>

              <Footer />
        </>
        
    )
}

export default App
